title: Some questions about dataset in scziDesk
body:
Hi Liang, I just wanna to use more real world data under scziDesk so I want to know where the original download link for the dataset is, for example the Quake_10x datasets. Can you give me the original download link or the URL？
THX！ :)

title: Example for Seurat and SC3 method
body: Hi, i am quite interested in your scziDesk method. However when i tried to re-run your results in the paper, i found it really hard to implement Seurat and SC3 method for dataset provided in your paper. Tutorials of Seurat and SC3 are mainly based on 10x dataset which has a different structure. So i wanna ask Do u have any example code of how could i implement Seurat/SC3 on your dataset?

title: 10X data sources
body:
36/5000 
May I ask whether the 10X data comes from the 10X official website? Why would it be wrong if I replace the data from the 10X official website？

title: About Geometric Anchor Correspondence Mining with Uncertainty Modeling for Universal Domain Adaptation
body:
Hi Liang, I am Shuo Wen from EPFL. I am super interested in your work _About Geometric Anchor Correspondence Mining with Uncertainty Modeling for Universal Domain Adaptation_. However, I need help finding the code. Could you please point me to the code of this paper?

Thank you in advance!

(Sorry to contact you this way. I did not manage to find your email.)
